summary: I figured I would share my bodyslide preset (better late than never).
descriptionHtml:
It's a simple bodyslide preset that shows off some pretty serious curves.

Comes with a nude and clothed preset with a bit of push-up.  You obviously need Bodyslide for this to work.  I recommend batch building with the clothed preset so all of your outfits will have the  push-up effect, then build your body with the nude preset.  If you like the facial preset, it is Wnisewand's Isabella preset you can get It here https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/88004.
author: Hambone
